      <h1 style="margin-top:10px">Pegboard, organiser or app: how to manage your club-night rotation</h1>
      <p class="lede">Every badminton club has to answer the same question all night: who plays next, and who with? There are really only a few ways clubs do it. Here is an honest comparison of each, and how to work out which one fits your club.</p>
