<section style="padding-top:40px">
  <div class="wrap" style="max-width:820px">
    <div class="guide-toc">
      <h4>In this guide</h4>
      <a href="#table">The approaches at a glance</a>
      <a href="#pegboard">The self-managed pegboard queue</a>
      <a href="#organiser">An organiser makes the games</a>
      <a href="#freeforall">Players arrange their own games</a>
